<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="exhibit-v">exhibit <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪɡ'zɪbɪt/    美 /ɪɡ'zɪbɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-show">1.★ <strong>展示；陈列；展览 (show)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This monument to him was first publicly exhibited in 1877. 
这座纪念他的塑像于1877年首次对公众展出。</p><footer>译林⑧ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Manufacturers are exhibiting their new model cars.
制造商在展示新车型。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-display">2.<strong>表现；显出 (display)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She exhibited no fear in the face of danger. 
面对危险她毫无惧色。</p></div></div>